dct_description_sm: Oriented with north toward bottom of sheet.
Index divided into 2 lower cartouches: Numerus et explicatio reru., locoru. ...
Decorative cartouches, coat of arms, elaborate compass rose, rhumb lines, ships, sea monsters.
Shows topography, vegetation, waterways, settlements, ports.
Dedication and extensive descriptive text in upper cartouche.
From Jasolino's De rimedi naturali che sono nell'Isola di Pithecusa..., Naples, 1588.
